Previously, Banaś was associated with NIK from 1992 to 2005., he acted in this institution as an associate of Lech Kaczyński.
During the first rule of PiS (2005-2008), Banas held the position of President of the Customs Service, and in addition, undersecretary of state in the Ministry of Finance.
